## 1667. FIX Names in a Table ##


# Problem Link - 
http://leetcode.com/problems/fix-names-in-a-table/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-sql-50

# Problem Statement -
Write a solution to fix the names so that only the first character is uppercase and the rest are lowercase.

Return the result table ordered by user_id.

# Query - 
select
    user_id,
    concat(upper(left(name, 1)), substr(name, 2))
from 
    Users
order by 
    user_id;